channel.title: Not working
channel.description:
I need some help with my server. It's working perfectly, but the coding is a little messed up.
Compile.bat is purring like a kitten. I can get into my server easily. My friend is a pro at making servers, so he helps me out. He says I can become an admin by changing my rights to 3. Easy. So I save it and stuff. Then I go back to my server, and nothing happened. I said "TESTING" and I didn't get a gold crown. I even tried ::banuser but still, nothing happened.
If it helps, I'm using TestScape. Anyone knows what I'm doing wrong?
